<br>
Im a thrust merc on Uk server Pydwen.  I am currently level 44.7 and am fully specced Thrust/Dw/Parry.<br>
<br>
At level 50 i am going 50 thrust, 50 Dual Wield and 28 Parry.<br>
<br>
As thrust mercs are very rare on my server id just like some advice. Is this spec very good? How do thrust mercs do in RvR? Any classes i should avoid?<br>
<br>
I have most people telling me that i am gimped because i am a saracen and because i have gone thrust. According to all the merc on my server highlander/slash/crush is the only way to go.<br>
<br>
Would like some input. i seem to do ok in RvR i think but wot is it like at end game.  I have struggled for months to get where i am because as you know a lot of mobs have high thrust resist. All in the hope that id be good in RvR.....if this is not the case then...........well....<br>
<br>
-Khendon McFlurry<br>
