<br>
What, exactly, are you giving up by going thrust as opposed to slash?  You'll have to make do without amethyst slash, the best anytime style in Albion (due mostly to its large to hit bonus and the value of the 50 diamond slash style that chains from it).  Additionally, the 50 thrust style, Dragonfang, is mostly useless to us, becuase our evade is less dependable than our parry.<br>
<br>
None of these things are reason enough to *not* spec thrust, if that's the way you want to play! <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=34.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=34.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=34.topic&index=7><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.emailToFriend?topicID=34.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.threadControl?topicID=34.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=34.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=34.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub79.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="lighttanksofdaocfrm9">Mercenary Equipment<option value="lighttanksofdaocfrm1">Blademaster General Discussion<option value="lighttanksofdaocfrm2">Mercenary General Discussion<option valu